{"tid":910744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普經濟顧問暗示「把中國踢出世貿組織」","createTime":"2018-11-21T11:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T17:29:45.000Z","uid":53379,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bc271d92a1e8af1921a758bbe987f0ea42691af3","tid":910744,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:39:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">特朗普經濟顧問暗示「把中國踢出世貿組織」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image1.thenewslens.com/2018/11/f16ybtqzog1w00nry5zkxcogn5iodg.jpg?auto=compress&amp;h=648&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage1.thenewslens.com%2F2018%2F11%2Ff16ybtqzog1w00nry5zkxcogn5iodg.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26h%3D648%26q%3D80%26w%3D1080&h=a053de62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普的經濟顧問凱文&middot;哈塞特（Kevin Hassett）在接受英國廣播公司（BBC）訪問時說，把中國從世界貿易組織（WTO）剔除並非完全不可能。<br />\n<br />\n哈塞特說，中國加入世貿之後「行為不端」：「我們從來沒有想過一個國家加入後會好像中國般表現，一個成員國竟然如此行為不端，對世貿而言確實是新鮮事。」<br />\n<br />\n他認為，現在的問題在於這情況是否可以透過雙邊談判解決，又或者改革世貿，甚至把中國踢走。哈塞特說，最後一個方案是最不願見到的，而他選擇以提問形式拋出來：「我們應否尋求把中國從世貿中剔除？」<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普在8月接受彭博資訊訪問時大力批評世貿是「有史以來最糟糕的貿易協議」，又說如果世貿再不改革，美國可能會退出。他的言論隨即引起議論紛紛，俄羅斯表示，如果落實，會對美國造成很大打擊。有分析更指這簡直是向中國送大禮，令中國夢想成真。如今則變成是踢中國出局。<br />\n<br />\n哈塞特在訪問中緊跟特朗普的調子，指世貿表現不濟，令美國失望，必須對不守規矩的成員施以嚴厲的懲罰。他說，美國的貿易壁壘總是低於其他成員國，以往的總統，包括布殊、克林頓和奧巴馬嘗試改善情況，卻做不到，如今特朗普在貿易問題上採取強硬策略卻是管用的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/108678?fbclid=IwAR28ftDKKnwXcyPEuubRfdQEQHI4w19kzepC1PNqk3LmAiwkKVqal8dnaqw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F108678%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR28ftDKKnwXcyPEuubRfdQEQHI4w19kzepC1PNqk3LmAiwkKVqal8dnaqw&d=dQXXU227e1GMxbmjVN7kGp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f8f20f77\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/108678?fbclid=IwAR28ftDKKnwXcyPEuubRfdQEQHI4w19kzepC1PNqk3LmAiwkKVqal8dnaqw</a>"},{"pid":"dba3ed2adc125d97e9c588712b9f0b4065821eea","tid":910744,"uid":199487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ba80a1ceb0d60bbc1367db29002d58af87dbf8","tid":910744,"uid":28309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:41:27.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b4b04190f3c7d8128fc99ebb257f31d738e7c0","tid":910744,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:43:21.000Z","msg":"23條，把刀架係頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a681701e68c8b80687a9ada2ac027a98f729e0c","tid":910744,"uid":106810,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"真心，咁易踢咩"},{"pid":"0a8d489bec75dd2b38494b88a91c6621ee85e17e","tid":910744,"uid":78143,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bJBqHL9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbJBqHL9.jpg&h=7362539c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"786b411f1a52c5ecfc06c3eed71fa42c681da662","tid":910744,"uid":34010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRzk-kwx3wMBliM1nBb-mrQxm6klHKiJXQ2xG8c3-Eo5ivA7SP0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcRzk-kwx3wMBliM1nBb-mrQxm6klHKiJXQ2xG8c3-Eo5ivA7SP0&h=b40c3fbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ed7f203741f70ac442e72b80892a2a76b8ef48f","tid":910744,"uid":222203,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e3a8408dde3e754b49261bd45345bc89202b2e7","tid